          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDG"
                ],
                "institute": "2SF HLS"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "2.5MV and 3.5MV Van de Graaff",
                "accelerators. The energy spread in the beams was of the",
                "order of 1 keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For absolute resonance stregth measurements:",
                "The Ne tagets were prepared by driving 3 keV 22Ne ions",
                "into tantalum backings."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " An 80 cm**3 Ge(Li) at a distance of 1 to 5 cm",
                "from the target , at an angle of 55 degree wich respect",
                "to the proton beam was used to detect the gamma-rays.",
                "The detector resolution was 2.6 keV at 1.33 MeV and 10",
                "keV at 10 MeV."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The excitation curve of the reaction was",
                "measured using a cylindrical 10x10 cm NaI detector set",
                "at an angle of 55 degree wich respect to the proton",
                "beam and at a distance of 4 cm from the target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In REACTIONs FCT=1/(2Jp+1)(2Jt+1),",
                "where is Jp = spin of incident projectile and",
                "Jt = spin of target nucleus.",
                "In the formula of resonance strength:",
                "          g*Gamma(i)Gamma(j)/Gamma(tot)",
                "instead of usual statistical weight:",
                "  g=(2J+1)/(2Jp+1)(2Jt+1), the authors used g=(2J+1)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error of 25% on the strengths is due to",
                "1) uncertainties in the areas of the resonance peaks,",
                "2) the relative efficiency of the NaI detector,",
                "3) the strength of the Ep=1280 keV resonance."
              ]
            }
          ],
